WEBVTT

00:00.010 --> 00:02.380
Previously on "Project Blue Book"...

00:02.400 --> 00:05.140
Our nation is suffering from
mass hysteria right now.

00:05.200 --> 00:08.039
We saw something in those
woods and it was real.

00:08.070 --> 00:11.250
You want me to investigate
flying saucers.

00:11.280 --> 00:12.620
Space ships, aliens,

00:12.640 --> 00:14.580
the Air Force knows they don't exist.

00:14.610 --> 00:16.450
The others that came believed me.

00:16.510 --> 00:19.060
- What others?
- The men in the hats.

00:20.220 --> 00:21.850
They left this for you.

00:22.980 --> 00:26.420
I think the doctor will perform
his role rather well, don't you?

00:26.440 --> 00:29.120
There's something off about him.

00:29.140 --> 00:32.159
I just didn't like him
asking so many questions.

